                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Key Highlights</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><span class="ok">Fair pay & documented invoices</span></li>
                        <li><span class="warn">Transparent taxes shown on bills</span></li>
                        <li><span class="ok">Standard margin: 50% (pre‑tax)</span></li>
                        <li><span class="ok">Print‑ready policy document</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Customization Tips</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Search for <code>Acme Services</code> and replace with your company name.</li>
                        <li>Adjust tax rate in the Pricing section.</li>
                        <li>Update schedule, benefits, and contact details.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

            </aside>
        </section>

        <footer>
            <div class="footer-grid">
                <div>Last updated: <strong>August 19, 2025</strong></div>
                <div>Authorized by: HR & Finance Departments</div>
                <div>© <span id="yr"></span> Acme Services (Pvt.) Ltd. All rights reserved.</div>
            </div>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <script>
        document.getElementById('yr').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
